Package wisedevil.credentials.export

This package contains classes to export encrypted credentials databases from/to disk or memory.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Exporter<T>
    This interface provides support for credentials exporters.
    Importer
    This interface provides support for credentials importers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WDCEncryptionRecord
    WDC encryption output and decryption input data.
    WDCExporter
    This class provides support for exporting a CredentialDatabase as a "WiseDevil Credentials" file format.
    WDCImporter
    This class provides support for importing a CredentialDatabase from a "WiseDevil Credentials" file.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DatabaseExportException
    This exception is thrown during the credential export process if an exception occurs.
    DatabaseImportException
    This exception is thrown during the credential import process if an exception occurs.

Package wisedevil.credentials.export Description

This package contains classes to export encrypted credentials databases from/to disk or memory.
